Ecommerce App REST API 
-----------------------------------
Admin stories
-------------
As an admin i should be able to login
As an admin i should be able to add products
As an admin i should be able to update products
As an admin i should be able to delete products
As an admin i should be able to approve refund

User stories
-------------
As a user i should be able to login
As a user i should be able too see all products
As a user i should be able to get producrs in sorting order of dates or price etc
As a user i should be able to add items to my cart
As a user i should be able to place order for my items
As a user i should be able to cancel my order
As a user i should be able to return my order


Entity Classes
---------------

User
Product
Cart
CartItem
Order
OrderItem
Payment
Refund



















